Document: GLTFTextureSampler  
Path: godot/classes/class_gltftexturesampler.rst  
Summary: Properties for configuring texture magnification, minification, and wrapping modes in GLTFTextureSampler.  

- **mag_filter** (int): Texture's magnification filter, used when texture appears larger on screen than the source image. Default: 9729. Set/Get: set_mag_filter(value: int), get_mag_filter().  
- **min_filter** (int): Texture's minification filter, used when the texture appears smaller on screen than the source image. Default: 9987. Set/Get: set_min_filter(value: int), get_min_filter().  
- **wrap_s** (int): Wrapping mode to use for S-axis (horizontal) texture coordinates. Default: 10497. Set/Get: set_wrap_s(value: int), get_wrap_s().  
- **wrap_t** (int): Wrapping mode to use for T-axis (vertical) texture coordinates. Default: 10497. Set/Get: set_wrap_t(value: int), get_wrap_t().